summary: Gives the sexy priestess of Dibella a makeover.
descriptionHtml:
Gives the sexy priestess of Dibella a makeover.  This is a simple mod that changes the look of Senna who you meet in the temple of Dibella.  She is my wife in Skyrim and I felt like sprucing her up a bit to my tastes.  I just thought I would share the mod in case anyone else likes the new look I gave her.  She didn\'t look that bad before, this is just my personal preference.  

By the way, I am using XCE\'s character enhancement with Better Females by Bella installed after XCE.  Also, I am using the makeup version 3 of Better Females by Bella with the no shine add on as well. Without these mods she won\'t look exactly like the pictures, but the changes will generally be the same.

To install just extract into your Skyrim folder or use NMM.
author: knuxson
